<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 lán tiān xià chéng qún de bái gē fēi,
 kǒu xián gǎn lǎn yè fēi dào nǐ nà lǐ qù.
 xiàng nǐ bào gào zuì hǎo de xiāo xī,
 shén ài shì rén, gèng ài shén zhōu ér nǚ.
 wǒ men dōu jǔ shǒu zàn měi shàng dì,
 zhōng guó zhōng yú zǒu xiàng shàng dì.
 wǒ men dōu jǔ shǒu gǎn xiè shàng dì,
 zhǔ a zhōng guó yào lái jìng bài nǐ.</lyrics>
<title>lán tiān xià chéng qún de bái gē fēi 迦南830</title>
<hymn_number>830</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>